msgid ""
"At its core, Mattermost is an open source alternative to proprietary SaaS"
" collaboration for teams. The software, developed in partnership with "
"thousands of contributors from around the world, is designed to increase "
"the agility, efficiency, and innovation in high trust organizations while"
" keeping data and operations under IT control."
msgstr ""

